Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:46.31,screen,,0,0,0,,{\an7\be1\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK_中\fs30\b1\frz7\c&HCB8E4E&\pos(715.238,422.666)}歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:46.31,screen,,0,0,0,,{\an7\be0.4\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK_中\fs40\frz7\c&HF0DBD6&\pos(917.066,487.2)}莫妮卡
